													"value": "AnimationTags"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Buddy's in a hostile pose growling, he lets off a bark after the dialogue. Please reuse HUM_M_Rig_CINE_Laugh_01 and HUM_M_Rig_DFLT_CINE_Cheer_Enthusiast_01 for crowd laughter. Children will be laughing while clapping. Dribbles' \"wa-hey\" to be a signature gesture to be used throughout the scene. <Gwen Lee>"
												}
											},
