												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Please reuse HUM_CHD_Rig_DFLT_SCENE_DEN_TrainingKids_OM_Wyll_AOM_CheeringBig_Child_04 and HUM_CHD_Rig_DFLT_SCENE_DEN_TrainingKids_OM_Wyll_AOM_CheeringSmall_Child_02 for the children at the front. Someone in the crowd can reuse HUM_M_Rig_DFLT_CINE_WeightShift_StandL_03. Intro of clown will be shot as custom anim, clown can be gathering the children in a \"come one, come all\" gesture.. <Gwen Lee>"
												}
